,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"屌你淋病"},{"pid":"5a2b87045fba95d6cc59cdf9e5869433b54077a8","tid":892869,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:04:19.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f716eb8fe0e1f129d7ccb95a3f4522e43800e0b","tid":892869,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ad264c975c444f16d1335c2c28ba06987d8089b","tid":892869,"uid":83914,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"逼d轉左加熱煙嘅人做番火車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"呢句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來我細佬食咗兩年幾電子煙，𠵱家就係淋病咁禁而做返火車頭"},{"pid":"fe58f1f366f4612ccc42e097001f3e3c6d931fe1","tid":892869,"uid":101732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:45:13.000Z","msg":"由於尼古丁為第一部毒藥成份，只能在藥房出售<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌你政府都on99<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ad7ca008e7f0563fd56c87695842916f964571b","tid":892869,"uid":46358,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:56:56.000Z","msg":"依家喺香港含尼古丁嘅電子煙一直都係犯法<br />\n<br />\n全禁真係得啖笑，先唔好講執法有幾難，邏輯一開始就已經唔通<br />\n<br />\n你為市民健康著想咁咪禁止販賣俾18歲以下人士囉，咪禁果味囉，你搞電子煙搞埋加熱煙啲人翻返去食傳統煙有幾健康呀？"},{"pid":"791f79b1a2d148f43b94ea0a8ad15ce8e2140a1e","tid":892869,"uid":83914,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"2f716eb8fe0e1f129d7ccb95a3f4522e43800e0b","tid":892869,"uid":2267,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2ad264c975c444f16d1335c2c28ba06987d8089b","tid":892869,"uid":83914,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T08:54:32.000Z","msg":"逼d轉左加熱煙嘅人做番火車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:42:28.000Z","msg":"呢句真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本來我細佬食咗兩年幾電子煙，𠵱家就係淋病咁禁而做返火車頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T09:59:56.000Z","msg":"根本會走去食加熱煙嘅人。佢地心裡會唔知食煙有害咩<br />\n<br />\n癮哩樣野有左咁易戒咩。旁人梗係會當佢地戇鳩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n竟然加熱煙傷害低咁多。而食個班又接受到用黎代替傳統煙<br />\n<br />\n對佢自己同旁人都好d。而又走去禁左佢。而唔係立法監管。<br />\n<br />\n政府就係知食哩類煙人數少。禁左都唔會有咩回響。嘈未由你地嘈幾日<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我本身係有食電子煙同加熱煙。電子煙對我黎講係玩具。講唔到可以戒煙嘅效果係度<br />\n<br />\n而加熱煙我覺得我可以大幅降低對煙嘅需求。<br />\n<br />\n食左十五年煙。轉左加熱煙一年。由每日傳統煙一包至包半到依家完全唔食<br />\n<br />\n煙彈一包。我一日最多食五支。依家即頭講明禁。我都無再買煙彈。食埋倉底就算。暫時就無再考慮食番傳統煙。但我唔保證會唔會食番<br />\n<br />\n我就話可能唔會食番煙做火車頭姐。但其他人係咪會做番火車頭逼人食二手煙先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0652ebbaa01c3c9eca27e110a8d30ec20e30f73","tid":892869,"uid":208417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95aa2d13865b871bdd9077c1f71b01d7a6e3adf","tid":892869,"uid":50253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"唔爭在禁埋煙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"無煙税 明大大嶼行唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ffe055902c11f0f662dd8c9d8670f2c519311f9","tid":892869,"uid":208417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0652ebbaa01c3c9eca27e110a8d30ec20e30f73","tid":892869,"uid":208417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a95aa2d13865b871bdd9077c1f71b01d7a6e3adf","tid":892869,"uid":50253,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T07:56:55.000Z","msg":"唔爭在禁埋煙"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:07:07.000Z","msg":"無煙税 明大大嶼行唔通<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T10:07:25.000Z","msg":"明日"},{"pid":"3d831c039d1785bf8a1dc91cdf8260e098b3413c","tid":892869,"uid":46358,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"隻故都幾唔掂<br />\n<br />\n明明喺講電子煙，啲字眼同條片就搞到好似講加熱煙咁<br />\n<br />\n明明就係兩樣嘢，啲人就成日撈埋一齊做瀨屎牛丸"},{"pid":"4dc73e690f1e20135d67f79bc01db9680f7b3250","tid":892869,"uid":92657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:48:21.000Z","msg":"條友係因為俾人周到電子煙啲尼古丁油，根本唔係加熱煙, 標題勁誤導囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n冇法律話用加熱煙係犯法囉，喺日本買煙彈返嚟乖乖交煙稅就可以合法入口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}